{"tid":332171,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"舊式雪條櫃　香港僅存兩部","createTime":"2017-07-22T18:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T06:21:35.000Z","uid":14730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"523871706b8f9e8076322a1e3be7106c24491dfb","tid":332171,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/025108_8e1e03167f7ac5acd393ab152776db2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F025108_8e1e03167f7ac5acd393ab152776db2b.jpg&h=01f24a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏天當然要吃雪條，拉開雪櫃門時，你有否留意過雪條櫃的設計？<br />\n<br />\n「這款雪櫃全港僅存兩部，維修員說，壞了也沒零件可換，要換新機。」士多老闆冬哥說。<br />\n<br />\n這款四四方方的雪條櫃安放在半山列堤頓道，相較新式矮身，高度剛好是小孩所及，一伸手便可輕易將兩道玻璃明由下而上斜推開。櫃的正面是一道雙層玻璃，讓一雙雙閃閃發亮的稚瞳窺探櫃內的繽紛世界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uLQish\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uLQish&d=3aNSw6jVxEDekNmPJGIa%2BHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e77f0ef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uLQish</a>"},{"pid":"9a398bd3f17c4d1468f42eb5eb6fb488f9a2daa8","tid":332171,"uid":54927,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"呢啲舊野有咩值得吹奏"},{"pid":"7a0e7d7648dc642a7cee0d3214d2a425e9b58a75","tid":332171,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"咁仲有幾多舊式汽水櫃?即係成個櫃裝住凍水浸住一支支汽水，已經好耐無見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695ff5e74b24d6ad5c939da73909ba5cc74f9ba2","tid":332171,"uid":92202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁仲有幾多舊式汽水櫃?即係成個櫃裝住凍水浸住一支支汽水，已經好耐無見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙角打邊爐 任飲汽水 就係呢種櫃"},{"pid":"abdbd72c2c2f30d4421e511fae50b6af962cef00","tid":332171,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20